result.formatted_address: 76 Po Tung Rd, Sai Kung, Hong Kong
result.name: Susanna's Seafood Restaurant

reviews.text:
One of the best choice in Sai Kung.
Very local traditional western dining steak house.
Price friendly, food fresh n service good.
A nice dining experience.

Whenever my US friend coming back, he definitely will go there and enjoy the food so much.Soup & the toast are always your best choice for the appritizer! Fried rice & seafood dishes will be your unforgetable choices too.Their service id so good that let you having the home feel.
This is one of the oldest restaurants in Sai Kung offering "soy source" steak.  We ordered lamb and pork chops today of which lamb was very good and tasty.  Price is a bit high but is good for value.
Great food! Great price! Great service!
Very good place for dinner

reviews.text: 餐廳比較舊但食物👍和價錢便宜

One of the best choice in Sai Kung.
Very local traditional western dining steak house.
Price friendly, food fresh n service good.
A nice dining experience.
舊式豉油西餐，食物麻麻，啲肉類點都好過花園果啲嘅，但幾樣嘢都冇厘味道，唔值。
鐵板牛扒麻麻地，肉質一般😅，價格有点不值😥
